# nepalcensus CRAN Submission Plan

## Package Summary
Data package: 89 datasets from Nepal Population and Housing Census 2021 (NPHC 2078 BS).
Source: National Statistics Office (NSO), Nepal.
23 Household (Hhld01–Hhld23) + 66 Individual (Indv01–Indv71, gaps at 08/12-15).

