## Dataset Column Patterns
All datasets share: prov, dist, gapa, provname, dname, gapaname, category, number
Additional columns by type:
- +sex/sexname: Hhld18, Indv06, Indv07 etc.
- +agegrp/agegrpname: Hhld14, Hhld16, Indv03 etc.
- +sex+agegrp: Hhld15, Hhld19-20, Hhld23, Indv09-11, Indv16-32, Indv52, Indv62, Indv66, Indv69
- +occ1/occname: Indv40-42, Indv55, Indv61, Indv64
- +ind1/indname: Indv43-45, Indv56-57, Indv65
- +litsts+edulvl/educationlevel: Indv37-39, Indv54, Indv58-59, Indv63, Indv67
- +wrkmon/workmonth: Indv49-51, Indv68
- +empsts/empstatus: Indv60
- +brthreg/brthregname: Indv71
- Special: Hhld13 (+tot_hhld, dead_hhld), Hhld17 (+tot_hhld, absnt_hhld), Indv01 (+n_hhld),
           Indv05 (+sizeclass/sizeclassname, num_locality, no_hhld), Indv36 (+chldtype/typename)

## User-Facing Functions
- catalog()           — returns datacatalog tibble; optional keyword search
- search_census(kw)   — alias/sugar for catalog(search = kw)
